JoyPlan privacy agreement
(Version of December January 26, 2024)
JoyPlan (hereinafter referred to as "we") knows the importance of personal information to you, and thank you for your trust in us. We will take corresponding security protection measures in accordance with laws and regulations and try our best to protect your personal information. . Based on this, Xiamen Zhibenjia Technology Co., Ltd., a provider of "JoyPlan" products and services, (hereinafter referred to as "Zhibenjia Company") formulated this Privacy Policy.
This policy mainly explains to you what information we collect, the purpose for which it is collected, your rights, etc., and affirms our commitment to protecting personal privacy. We may update or modify this policy in the future based on changes in the information processing context. Please be aware of this policy and any supplementary policies before using any services provided by JoyPlan.
This policy applies to "JoyPlan" products and services, including "JoyPlan" IOS software client, "JoyPlan" Android software client, and "JoyPlan" other forms of carriers.
We are committed to maintaining your trust in us, and abide by the following principles to protect your personal information: the principle of consistency of rights and responsibilities, the principle of clear purpose, the principle of choice and consent, the principle of least adequateness, the principle of ensuring security, the principle of subject participation, the principle of openness and transparency, etc. . At the same time, we promise that we will take appropriate security measures to protect your personal information in accordance with the industry's mature security standards.
Before using "JoyPlan" products or services, you must read and understand the entire contents of this policy. Once you start using "JoyPlan" products or services, you fully understand and agree to this policy.
If you have any questions, comments or suggestions about the content of this policy, please contact us through the method at the end of the article.
